    "The SSRIT framework by Chi et al. (2021) suggests that the readiness of customers in engaging with robots may be impacted by their confidence in human-robot interaction.",
    "People who experience perceived credibility tend to put their faith in others because of their admirable behaviors (Singh and Sinha, 2020).",
